  {
    "id": "SQ-02",
    "title": "The Overgrown Silo",
    "xp_reward": 600,
    "prerequisites": "None",
    "description": "Grain Silo 4 has been claimed by a nocturnal infestation of 'Star-Ivy', pulsing with an otherworldly lavender glow.",
    "turns": [
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "narrative": "Under the moon's pale eye, the silo looks like a gargantuan tumor of vine and leaf. The ivy doesn't just grow; it writhes, the sound of rubbing leaves mimicking a dry whisper.",
        "choice_a": "Auscultate the vines (Nature DC 12)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You hear the sap-flow, realizing it's synchronized with the ley-lines. (+1 Lore)",
        "choice_b": "Prune a path with a silvered blade (Athletics DC 13)",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The vines bleed a glowing violet sap as you carve a path to the door. (+1 Progress)",
        "convergence": "The maintenance door groans, held shut by the weight of the growth."
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "narrative": "Sap has filled the keyhole and fused the hinges. The smell is sweet, almost intoxicating, reminding you of a childhood garden you never had.",
        "choice_a": "Sledgehammer the hinges (Strength DC 15)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The metal screams and gives way, showering you in cold, bioluminescent nectar. (+1 Progress)",
        "choice_b": "Burn the sap with a controlled torch",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The sap flares blue and vanishes, but the heat damages the internal mechanisms. (-1 Resource)",
        "convergence": "You step into the silo. The air is thick with floating spores that shimmer like snowfall."
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "narrative": "Internal humidity is near 100%. Your breath comes in ragged gasps through the spore-fog. Every step on the grain feels like walking on a graveyard.",
        "choice_a": "Steady your breathing (Con Save DC 12)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You maintain your focus as the spores try to seed in your lungs.",
        "choice_b": "Improvise a filter mask from salt-cloth",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The acrid salt neutralizes the sweetness. Safe passage.",
        "convergence": "At the center of the grain-pile, a massive 'Star-Heart' bulb pulses with a rhythmic light."
      },
      {
        "turn": 4,
        "narrative": "The bulb is the source—fed by a network of root-ropes that have drained the grain of all nutrient value.",
        "choice_a": "LANCE the bulb's core (Attack AC 10)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: A spray of violet gas erupts as the core shrivels. (+1 Item)",
        "choice_b": "Salt the root-vines (Herbalism DC 14)",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The vines turn black and brittle within seconds. (+2 Progress)",
        "convergence": "A screech echoes from the catwalks above—the keepers of the harvest are unhappy."
      },
      {
        "turn": 5,
        "narrative": "Gloom-Rats, their fur replaced by tiny glowing sprouts, scurry along the rusted pipes. Their eyes are frantic, violet pinpricks in the dark.",
        "choice_a": "Ignite a 'Sun-Flare' (Spell/Cantrip)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The rats are blinded, tumbling from the heights. (+1 Tactical Adv)",
        "choice_b": "Trust your ears (Survival DC 12)",
        "consequence_b": "Success: You hear the tail-drag and dodge the first pounce. (+1 Progress)",
        "convergence": "Three mutated rats land in the grain around you, baring teeth that glow like hot coals."
      },
      {
        "turn": 6,
        "narrative": "The rats are connected by thin, glowing threads of ivy. They move with a terrifyingly singular purpose.",
        "choice_a": "Sever the connecting ivy (Dex DC 14)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The rats lose their coordination, snapping at each other in confusion. (+Damage)",
        "choice_b": "Intimidate the swarm (Intimidation DC 14)",
        "consequence_b": "Failure: The rats feel no fear, only the hunger of the ivy.",
        "convergence": "The lead rat lunges for your throat."
      },
      {
        "turn": 7,
        "narrative": "Combat is a blur of fur and fangs in the violet-lit dark.",
        "choice_a": "Sweeping Area Attack",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You clear a circle of safety around you, severing multiple vines. (+100 XP)",
        "choice_b": "Target the alpha rat (Attack AC 12)",
        "consequence_b": "Success: You pin the alpha to the wall, causing the others to flee back into the shadows.",
        "convergence": "The rats yield. The silo falls into a heavy, sap-scented silence."
      },
      {
        "turn": 8,
        "narrative": "In the corner of the rat-nest, you see the glint of metal—remnants of the worker who went missing last month.",
        "choice_a": "Sift through the nest",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You find a 'Ridge-Walker's Signet' and a handful of coin. (+1 Loot)",
        "choice_b": "Burn the infestation with oil",
        "consequence_b": "Success: You ensure the ivy has no refuge to return to. (+1 Morale)",
        "convergence": "You climb the ladder to the upper vents to secure the perimeter."
      },
      {
        "turn": 9,
        "narrative": "The moon is setting. To finish the job, the ground outside must be treated to prevent re-emergence.",
        "choice_a": "Spread quick-lime around the silo foundation",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The ph-shift kills the remaining root-nodes. (+1 Stability)",
        "choice_b": "Install 'Glow-Warding' lamps on the exterior",
        "consequence_b": "Success: A modern defense for a modern blight. (-1 Battery)",
        "convergence": "The farmer, a man named Harlen, approaches with a lantern and a look of hope."
      },
      {
        "turn": 10,
        "narrative": "Harlen hands you a small pouch of silver, his hands shaking. He knows the silos are the settlement's lifeblood.",
        "choice_a": "Accept the coin (50 Gold)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You are paid for your labor. (+50 Gold)",
        "choice_b": "Decline the coin but take the 'Star-Ivy' samples",
        "consequence_b": "Success: Your reputation for selflessness grows, and you have rare material for alchemy. (+2 Reputation)",
        "convergence": "Quest Complete."
      }
    ],
    "conclusion": "Silo 4 is secured. The grain is safe, though the 'Star-Ivy' seeds found in the rat nest hint at a deliberate sabotage.",
    "loot_table": [
      "Star-Heart Bulb",
      "Ridge-Walker Signet Ring",
      "Glow-Rat Pelt",
      "100 Gold"
    ],
