  {
    "id": "SQ-04",
    "title": "The Rat King's Crown",
    "xp_reward": 800,
    "prerequisites": {
      "quests_completed": [
        "SQ-28"
      ],
      "items_required": [
        "Concordat ID Ring"
      ],
      "district_reputation": {},
      "status_effects": []
    },
    "description": "A blockade of 'shining refuse' has jammed the main drain of the High Ward, and the sewer-scouts report 'voices in the dark'.",
    "turns": [
      {
        "turn": 1,
        "narrative": "The sewers of Warden-Keep are a labyrinth of weeping stone and the smell of ancient decay. The blockage isn't just trash; it's a meticulously constructed dam of silverware and bone.",
        "choice_a": "Navigate the effluent flow (Con Save DC 12)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You keep your footing in the oily water, avoiding the sickness of the pipes. (+1 Progress)",
        "choice_b": "Apply a sweet-smelling oil to your mask",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The scent of jasmine masks the ammonia, keeping your head clear. (+1 Progress)",
        "convergence": "You reach the main cistern, where millions of small, yellow eyes watch you from the shadows."
      },
      {
        "turn": 2,
        "narrative": "The 'dam' is built from the stolen wealth of the Upper Ward. You see rings, spoons, and even a ceremonial mace woven into the sludge.",
        "choice_a": "Inspect the markings on the silver (Investigation DC 12)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: You recognize the crest of House Valerius—this wasn't just theft, it was a raid. (+1 Lore)",
        "choice_b": "Sunder the blockade with a heavy pick (Strength DC 13)",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The dam breaks, releasing a torrent of water and a chorus of angry squeaks. (+1 Stability)",
        "convergence": "As the water recedes, a massive albino rat, the size of a mountain lion, steps into the light."
      },
      {
        "turn": 3,
        "narrative": "The Rat King wears a crown of fused copper wire and a glowing sapphire ring. Its tail has been replaced by a silver chain. It doesn't hiss; it speaks into your mind.",
        "choice_a": "Offer a tribute of dried meat (Animal Handling DC 13)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The creature's hunger is sated, and its psychic pressure relaxes. (+1 Diplo)",
        "choice_b": "Intimidate the 'Abomination' with fire",
        "consequence_b": "Success: The rats cower, but their King's eyes burn with a hateful intelligence. (+1 Tactical Adv)",
        "convergence": "The Rat King speaks: 'The surface-men take the sun. We take the shine. Balance, little knight. Balance.'"
      },
      {
        "turn": 4,
