        "convergence": "Warden Artificer Soli Yan arrives with a spectroscope and tests the moth-dust. 'Warp-Static residue,' she says, 'combined with extracted enchantment mana.' She looks up. 'Something is dissolving enchantments and taking the mana somewhere. The moths are the mechanism. The question is: what needs this much mana, and why is it in the Market Ward boutiques?'"
