        "choice_a": "Enter the warehouse carefully and observe before engaging (Stealth DC 12)",
        "consequence_a": "Success: The interior is extraordinary. The moth colony covers every surface—thousands of Fabric-Eater Moths, each about the size of a thumb, with wings that shift through colors in the Warp-Static spectrum. In the center of the colony, a mound of crystallized mana the size of a barrel, still growing. They are farming it. This is a mana-production operation. (+1 Lore)",
