        "convergence": "Yan files her official report: 'Fabric-Eater Moth colony operating as Concordat-era enchantment-mana harvesting system. Infrastructure integration confirmed. Medical/magical hazard: moderate. Property damage: significant to boutique district. Conclusion: the Concordat left behind a city full of things still running their last instructions.' She hands you your copy of the report and adds: 'I am going to take a week off after this.'"
